{
  "stem": "19895.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 132.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I never talked much about my experiences until this interview.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My family knows tidbits about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there is not everything one can tell in a few hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I try to summarize it as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The feelings of being humiliated for your religion, for your race, I was Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My race, I thought it was just a different religion I had, but I was very Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I loved every bit of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Just like many of the Hungarian Jews, we sort of wanted to be Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so it was for German Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were more German from what I understand than-- than many of the German so-called [? aria, ?] which means the chosen race of the upper, the-- the top race.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The Germans thought that there is nobody like them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I just would like to say that it cannot be erased from one's memory, never, what I went through.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But as-- as years go by, I opened up a little more to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And on the urging of my daughters and my wife, I agreed to give this interview.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I-- I would see that I was controlling my emotions as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I worked in hospital for 35 years where few people hardly knew about all of this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I never talked much about my concentration camp experiences or the Jewish experience of growing up in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Because I wanted them to look at me as a-- an individual whom they don't feel pity or sorry for, that part of his life was so horrible and terrible.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- and I kept very silent about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I think that's how I wanted it to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "On the other hand, I am now 68 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
